      "latex": "",
      "raw": "For a monthly period loan with gross principal \\(L\\), monthly rate \\(i\\), and term \\(n\\): Serviced interest payment each month: \\[ I_m = L \\cdot i \\] Retained interest deducted upfront: \\[ I_{\\text{retained}} = L \\cdot i \\cdot n \\] Rolled-up balance at redemption: \\[ B_n = L\\,(1+i)^n \\] Exit fee (percent of gross loan \\(e\\%\\)): \\[ \\text{Exit} = L \\cdot \\frac{e}{100} \\] APR is the monthly internal rate of return \\(r\\) that solves: \\[ 0 = -\\,\\text{NetAdvance} + \\sum_{t=1}^{n} \\text{Pay}_t\\,(1+r)^{-t} + \\text{Redemption}\\,(1+r)^{-n} \\] with annualisation \\( \\text{APR} = (1+r)^{12} - 1 \\)."
    }
